Class OntologyManagerImpl

java.lang.Object
org.biopax.psidev.ontology_manager.impl.OntologyManagerImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
OntologyManager
public class OntologyManagerImpl extends Object implements OntologyManager
Access to the specified bio/chem ontologies (loaded from several OBO format files).
Since:
2.0.0
Author:
Florian Reisinger, Samuel Kerrien (skerrien@ebi.ac.uk), rodche (baderlab.org) - simplified it for BioPAX Validator

      public Set<OntologyTermI> searchTermByName(String name, Set<String> ontologies)
      Description copied from interface: OntologyManager
      Search for terms by name or synonym. The search is case insensitive. It still iterates over all available ontologies, but skips ones other than specified in the second parameter.
